name: MySpace Design Template
description:
The old tired work horse. As long as Google™ still ranks MySpace™ Band Pages at the top of it's list, bands still need good looking profiles. Features:
  • Photoshop Friendly File (.psd)
  • Guide layers for Standard and Extended Marquees
  • Layers are combined based on the MySpace editor
  • Photoshop column rules for adding your own modules
*Ad Nauseam is in no way affiliated with MySpace™ or any of its partners. All trademarks are property of their respective owners ** IMPORTANT NOTE: This is a TEMPLATE not a THEME. It is strictly to aid you in designing a profile, not building it.
